entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Yè li te Gunther Street. Koulye a, yo ap limen isit la, tou." t="Yesterday it was Gunther Street. Now they're lighting up here, too." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Nou ta dwe vide gaz sou yo. Boule yo tankou balèn." t="We should pour gas on the little shits. Burn 'em like candles." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou panse li jis kèk timoun estipid?" t="Think it might be just some stupid kids?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li evidan. Ou pa?" t="Obviously. You don't?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Petèt yon moun vle fè nou pè." t="Maybe someone wants to scare us off." b="" a=""/>
